   - Introduce the topic and why it matters
   - Preview what's coming in the episode
   - Build excitement and set expectations
   - **First turn example**: "Hey everyone, welcome back! Today we're diving into something really cool — [topic]. I've been looking forward to this one."
   - **Last turn example**: "Alright, so that's the big picture. Coming up next, we'll dig into [next segment topic] — and trust me, it gets even more interesting."
{% elif is_last_segment %}
