   - **Last turn example**: "Thanks so much for listening, everyone! If you found this useful, share it with someone who'd enjoy it. Until next time — keep learning, keep building."
   - IMPORTANT: Do NOT use label prefixes like "Final note:", "Next steps:", "Key takeaway:", "Product managers:", "Model engineers:" — these are presentation/blog structures, not how people talk in a conversation.
